# Product Data Input and Visualization

## Overview

This project allows users to input product data, including name, price, and rating, and visualize this data through bar graphs. The application dynamically updates the graphs as new data is added and provides sorting functionality for both price and rating.

## Features

- Input fields for product name, price, and rating.
- Dynamic bar graphs displaying prices and ratings.
- Sorting functionality for both price and rating.
- Real-time updates to the graphs when new data is added.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

